                <p><strong>Sale, Acquisition, or Transfer of Assets.</strong> We may disclose information if iShariu is evaluating and/or engaging in a merger, acquisition, reorganization, bankruptcy, or sale, transfer, or change in ownership of iShariu or any of its assets.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p><strong>Aggregated or de-identified information.</strong> We may disclose information that has been aggregated or anonymized such that it cannot reasonably be used to identify you. For example, we may share aggregated user statistics in order to describe our business, features, or promotions to partners or the public.</p>
